y #bonemets #bonemetastasis #breastcancer #metastaticbreastcancer #metastaticcancer #stage4cancer #cancer #chronicillness #walkingaid";}i:147;a:1:{s:14:"comments_count";i:0;}i:148;a:1:{s:11:"likes_count";i:0;}i:149;a:1:{s:4:"link";s:39:"https://www.instagram.com/p/CEvNpfGJB-b";}i:150;a:1:{s:5:"image";s:250:"https://scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/p1080x1080/118946136_2597344490482751_5910200460460773385_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=111&_nc_ohc=HmU6ieCPydkAX8p1e2h&oh=1ad0a0481bbb7a7eab62ffea5b921410&oe=5F7C7D63";}i:151;a:1:{s:4:"type";s:5:"image";}i:152;a:1:{s:8:"owner_id";i:3053670513;}i:153;a:1:{s:14:"owner_username";s:0:"";}i:154;a:1:{s:14:"owner_fullname";s:0:"";}i:155;a:1:{s:9:"owner_pic";s:0:"";}i:156;a:1:{s:2:"id";s:19:"2391189696889758270";}i:157;a:1:{s:10:"short_code";s:11:"CEvNlw5sCI-";}i:158;a:1:{s:12:"created_time";i:1599272046;}i:159;a:1:{s:7:"caption";s:294:"MICROGREENS - My brother has the green thumb, not me, but I am going to do my best to keep this little guy alive!

